{"tid":2085450,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPad Pro A12Z Geekbench跑分超Surface Pro X，GPU效能僅次於千元顯示卡","createTime":"2020-06-30T01:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T00:08:18.000Z","uid":109923,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0c90eb2d54d13ccc4ea9794f3df5a277c852430e","tid":2085450,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果DTK 開發套件，也就是那台搭載了A12Z 仿生晶片的DTK Mac mini 已經到達了很多開發者手中，我們也看到了A12Z 的跑分。根據Geekbench 的多個跑分，DTK A12Z 的單核平均分為811，多核平均分2871。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/stroughtonsmith/status/1277628592458006528?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstroughtonsmith%2Fstatus%2F1277628592458006528%3Fs%3D20&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=9df03eb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstroughtonsmith%2Fstatus%2F1277628592458006528%3Fs%3D20&h=3110e57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/stroughtonsmith/status/1277628592458006528?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n根據開發者Steve Troughton-Smith 提示，DTK Mac mini 中搭載的這顆A12Z晶片與2018款iPad Pro中的A12X相同，只是多開啟了一顆GPU核心，但其效能已經擊敗了微軟ARM 晶片Surface Pro X，而且A12Z 還是通過Rosetta 2 轉譯的x86_64 代碼。Surface Pro X 運行的是原生ARM 應用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ianbetteridge/status/1277616209173843969?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianbetteridge%2Fstatus%2F1277616209173843969%3Fs%3D20&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=2201d8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianbetteridge%2Fstatus%2F1277616209173843969%3Fs%3D20&h=4b51965c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ianbetteridge/status/1277616209173843969?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n微軟Surface Pro X 的Geekbench 跑分單核726，多核2831，這意味著A12Z 單核分數超越Surface Pro X，多核分數也略高於Surface Pro X。<br />\n<br />\nSurface Pro X搭載微軟設計的3GHz ARM晶片，這顆晶片基於高通SQ1芯片開發。蘋果DTK中的A12Z晶片與2018款iPad Pro中的A12X相同，只是多開啟了一顆GPU核心。<br />\n<br />\n未來，將要出現在Mac電腦上的ARM晶片將基於A14晶片開發，A14晶片採用5納米工藝，會在2020年iPhone上首次亮相。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示，自研晶片提供更高的效能、更低耗電、更少發熱。"},{"pid":"6ba7cba2b6895907134e850918e1e4dc5684233b","tid":2085450,"uid":52311,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"arm無x86堆指令集 得跑分有鳩用咩"},{"pid":"453ee2db1b301e90f9a7590da6f264ee9f2e476b","tid":2085450,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"就現場演示來看Shadow of the Tomb Raider的效果，畫質絕對不是low，大概有中畫質，FPS不清楚，但影片中在小型場景基本順暢當有30FPS，A12Z的GPU效能介乎960M與GTX1050之間，接近有千元顯示卡的效能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAbyx0u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAbyx0u.jpg&h=adff7ff7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f247c9892aeab201fa37a721243efb9dc805160","tid":2085450,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"Ipad 幾時可以裝windows app<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5374eddecc6b08cca61cde372913f6f2cc889871","tid":2085450,"uid":109923,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"多核都夠打i3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUkWvPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUkWvPP.jpg&h=4ab4f75f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adfd260ae62b6b962022962cf30d983678d2eb68","tid":2085450,"uid":109923,"like":26,"dislike":6,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"6ba7cba2b6895907134e850918e1e4dc5684233b","tid":2085450,"uid":52311,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"arm無x86堆指令集 得跑分有鳩用咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"Rosetta 2 於安裝x86_64 native程式時已直接轉譯成arm-native<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有arm版microsoft office、有arm版adobe、呢度已經滿足大部份普通用家嘅需求<br />\n<br />\n遲啲arm mac + metal api仲會迎來更多遊戲，豐富返mac